{"tid":1550731,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"大公報=藍絲 支那01=左膠","createTime":"2019-09-07T17:22:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T23:28:58.000Z","uid":135475,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"dc6d0d2d192a6e79b01494f86abe719a005cc20d","tid":1550731,"uid":135475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:22:15.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屌你老母<br />\n都係陰啲陰啲<br />\n背後捅你一刀<br />\n</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"9d40acaf113becc7572785f69dedf76210370ece","tid":1550731,"uid":252492,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:22:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">左膠永遠都唔係同路人<br />\n<br />\n荃灣黑夜 要前線放藍衫走<br />\n結果同一班藍衫轉頭斬斷其他手足手筋腳筋攪到個手足殘廢 同有手足比人爆頭<br />\n到今日岩岩機場 逼手足放個用磚頭爆手足頭既藍絲走<br />\n<br />\n重有依2個月好多單左膠死攬傷人者<br />\n根本班撚樣只係為光環 欺善怕惡<br />\n對住黑社會就淆底唔敢阻黑社會斬人<br />\n對住自己手足 知手足唔會打佢地<br />\n就大大力阻手足還拖 同講廢話訓前線話<br />\n話會扣幾多分 會失民意<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"3d36445c4e46f7232a4f1541b9c638b3e5ff2dd6","tid":1550731,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:22:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"801b044521f7313f7112d039ee02d1f2b78a2f8d","tid":1550731,"uid":113373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:22:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ORetRaw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FORetRaw.jpg&h=85231497&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"356f395a7c7cb7a792efe981f0a4e3164022b7af","tid":1550731,"uid":135475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:23:10.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3397dbd1dd8d8da30a45d5f065cf8adf8a7b0630","tid":1550731,"uid":254558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:25:15.000Z","msg":"【修訂版】元朗9.9七點三有人鏈<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1550636\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1550636</a>"},{"pid":"6a00dd85015e1ef3f2ab89652c1a04dbf062185e","tid":1550731,"uid":305294,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:45:16.000Z","msg":"係咪仲有人唔知01紅底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79d9882988613bdf14e2111482bed68e60eb3f29","tid":1550731,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T20:28:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">左膠永遠都唔係同路人<br />\n<br />\n荃灣黑夜 要前線放藍衫走<br />\n結果同一班藍衫轉頭斬斷其他手足手筋腳筋攪到個手足殘廢 同有手足比人爆頭<br />\n到今日岩岩機場 逼手足放個用磚頭爆手足頭既藍絲走<br />\n<br />\n重有依2個月好多單左膠死攬傷人者<br />\n根本班撚樣只係為光環 欺善怕惡<br />\n對住黑社會就淆底唔敢阻黑社會斬人<br />\n對住自己手足 知手足唔會打佢地<br />\n就大大力阻手足還拖 同講廢話訓前線話<br />\n話會扣幾多分 會失民意<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"4ac4f80aa586a03c33b1c931daa884a8a0d3e890","tid":1550731,"uid":60434,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T20:30:02.000Z","msg":"01黨媒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"950ffe4a69e213342be52289f2276a8da2b49175","tid"